Our Coral Pink and Off White Gharara Suit has been painstakingly curated against a coral pink net canvas with a silverish sheen to it. The element that stand out the most on the shirt is the hem which features tracery frameworks carrying a floral vase inside. The neatly worked neckline and  a generous spray of bootis on the daman adds a spring-like subtlety. The outfit has been paired with an embroidered gharara and a tulle dupatta with elaborate embellishments and finished with a silver gota lace.
Shop now exclusively at Lashkaraa.com

Enchanting and mesmerising, our Red Orange and Maroon Peplum Suit is redefining traditional aesthetics. The bodice is emblazoned with floral and vine shaped motifs in  beautiful shades of orange, silver and dull gold. The flare features elaborate bouquet patterns which are a reminiscent of mughal miniature art. The hem has been finished with a multi-layered border comprising of dainty and heavily-worked laces. The same embellishments have been meticulously rendered on the maroon dupatta to enhance the overall design.
Shop now exclusively at Lashkaraa.com
